Class BentWireActive

  • java.lang.Object
    • dangerzone.blocks.Block

        • blocks.BentWire

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PoweredComponent

    public class BentWireActive
extends BentWire
    Active bent wires are the active form of bent wires. A bent wire becomes active when supplied with at least 1 power. As soon as power is exhausted, a bent wire will become inactive again. This glow effect is entirely aesthetic, and supplies no illumination.

    Active bent wires, as technical blocks, are not obtainable in-game through any means.

    eaglgenes101
